Task: Create UnitProgressCard component

Summary: Implemented UnitProgressCard component for displaying unit completion status with lesson breakdown.

Changes:
- Created components/dashboard/UnitProgressCard.tsx with:
  - Unit number and title display
  - Progress bar with percentage
  - Lesson breakdown (completed of total)
  - Status indicator (In Progress/Completed)
  - Color coding: orange for in-progress, green for completed
  - Icon indicators (Clock for in-progress, CheckCircle for completed)
  - Proper ARIA attributes for accessibility (progressbar role)
- Updated components/dashboard/index.ts to export UnitProgressCard
- Created comprehensive test suite (__tests__/components/dashboard/UnitProgressCard.test.tsx) with 13 tests covering:
  - Unit metadata rendering (number, title)
  - Progress bar width and behavior (0%, 100%, intermediate values)
  - Lesson breakdown display
  - Completion state handling
  - Accessibility (ARIA roles and labels)
  - Edge cases (single lesson, many lessons)

Why: Unit progress cards help both students and teachers track progress through course units at a glance, providing clear visual feedback on completion status.

Files created/modified:
- components/dashboard/UnitProgressCard.tsx (new)
- components/dashboard/index.ts (modified)
- __tests__/components/dashboard/UnitProgressCard.test.tsx (new)
